  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "Go fishing in the great outdoors with Bass Hunter 64! Reel in a record-setting bass in tournament mode in 3D rendered environments, complete with native wildlife, and geographically accurate landscapes. Fish Pennsylvania's Lake Arthur and Florida's Butler Chain Lakes. Lure, strike, and fish-fighting animations are designed to simulate bass fishing's most exciting moments.",
